<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA1">
<l>aṉpē takaḷiyā vārvamē neyyāka</l>
<l>viṉpuruku cintai yiṭutiriyā – naṉpuruki</l>
<l>ñāṉac cuṭarviḷak kēṟṟiṉē ṉāraṇaṟku</l>
<l>ñāṉat tamiḻpurinta nāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Love as bowl, devotion as oil,</l>
<l>the mind melting with bliss as a wick to be put, well melting,</l>
<l>I lifted the glowing lamp of cognition,</l>
<l>I who made expert Tamil for Nāraṇaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
